    "text": "January 14 brought us an insane aurora, the longest and most intense I\u2019ve seen in Stockholm since 2015! I took about 2000 images from downtown and my balcony. Please see the reel for this particular \u2018show\u2019 over Riddarholmen and Gamla Stan. #viewstockholm #sweden_images #loves_united_scandinavia  #igscstockholm  #igs_europe #ig_europe #loves_sweden #bestcitybreaks  #loves_united_europe #topeuropephotos #sweden_photolovers  #igworld_global #loves_united_sweden #worlds_beautiful_photos #stockholm_insta #awesome_phototrip #best_worldplaces  #bestcaptureglobal #best_worldplaces #exceptional_pictures #divine_worldplaces #world_photo_shots #aurora #worldaurora #ig_auroraborealis #auroraborealis #auroraborealisnotifications #astrophotography #umeaaurorahunters #northernlightsphotos #northernlights @sweden",
